{"id":694033,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/694033.html","date":"2023-03-20T09:55:00Z","modified":"2023-03-20T09:55:00Z","title":"晖常有思｜网友们画出了现代版的孔乙己故事","content":"<p><iframe title=\"2023.3.20 《生活在一线城市的当代大学生孔乙己》\" width=\"1080\" height=\"810\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/fZXF9E6GcZo?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p>这两天，孔乙己文学一下子火了，孔乙己这个人物于是也被人们重新想起来了，他的命运，他的遭遇，无不让人们为之悠悠叹口气了。</p>\n<p>如果换个时空，孔乙己到了现代又会发生怎样的故事呢？有网友沿着这个脑洞，于是构思了一个新的故事，并画出来了。</p>\n<p>一百年后，故事的场景不再是咸亨酒店，而是帝都郊区的城中村了。</p>\n<div style=\"width:42%;float:right;padding-left:20px;\">\n<div class=\"su-spoiler su-spoiler-style-fancy su-spoiler-icon-chevron-circle su-spoiler-closed\" data-scroll-offset=\"0\" data-anchor-in-url=\"no\"><div class=\"su-spoiler-title\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\"><span class=\"su-spoiler-icon\"></span>CDT 档案卡</div><div class=\"su-spoiler-content su-u-clearfix su-u-trim\">\n<strong>标题：</strong>网友们画出了现代版的孔乙己故事<br />\n<strong>作者：</strong>小晖<br />\n<strong>来源：</strong><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/IVM-S0IgTe9TrHLnI1Jeaw\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">微信公众号“晖常有思”</a><br />\n<strong>发表日期：</strong>2023.3.20<br />\n<strong>主题归类：</strong><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/tag/孔乙己文学\" target=\"_blank\">孔乙己文学</a><br>\n<strong>CDS收藏：</strong><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E9%A6%86\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">公民馆</a><br>\n<strong>版权说明：</strong>该作品版权归原作者所有。中国数字时代仅对原作进行存档，以对抗中国的网络审查。<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/copyright\">详细版权说明</a>。\n</div></div>\n</div>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/03/post-694033-64182d7486973.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>那个卖酒的小伙计变成收租的了。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/03/post-694033-64182d749c47c.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>这时候，孔乙己登场了。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/03/post-694033-64182d74b187a.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>依旧说着让人听不懂的话。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/03/post-694033-64182d74c7b21.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>在这个时代中，孔乙己毕业于国内工科大学。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/03/post-694033-64182d74dd34d.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>不过命运并没有改变，依然要被熟识的人取笑。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/03/post-694033-64182d74f1c44.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>之乎者也换成了越老越吃香。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/03/post-694033-64182d7510771.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>空气依然是快活的。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/03/post-694033-64182d752098e.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>连收租的父亲也总是打趣他。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/03/post-694033-64182d7533a87.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>跟小孩子聊天时，茴香豆换成了高考。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/03/post-694033-64182d7547146.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>他让小孩子争取考个好大学。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/03/post-694033-64182d755b5e5.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>结果还是被怼回去了。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/03/post-694033-64182d7570e4e.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/03/post-694033-64182d7583bf2.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>在这个故事中，孔乙己依旧欠房租。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/03/post-694033-64182d7598a37.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>听旁人说，他回老家了。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/03/post-694033-64182d75adc5d.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>回老家后，进厂打工了。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/03/post-694033-64182d75c3a79.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/03/post-694033-64182d75d49a5.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>一气之下，孔乙己于是去考公了。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/03/post-694033-64182d75e8702.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>看着这样的孔乙己新编故事，既让人惊叹于网友们的脑洞，也让人不由感慨于孔乙己的命运，如何才能让孔乙己们不再愁眉，而是真正可以找到适合自己的路，让一生所学不至于成为屠龙之技。</p>\n<p>这真的需要我们社会管理者去好好考虑下。</p>\n","author":1069,"categories":[45870,41492,43134],"tags":[46656,40255,43587,45375,46647]}